{"tid":2471293,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚引玉］有邊間漢堡包好食","createTime":"2021-04-01T12:05:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T13:30:21.000Z","uid":220794,"like":12,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"a2196e9f925ab9d9c0543d1d043f10194b072d94","tid":2471293,"uid":220794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T12:05:51.000Z","msg":"最近睇劉浩龍同埋Eric Kwok 介紹漢堡包，<br />\n睇完心思思都想食，於是乎就揀左 鄰居。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSGRiJE9aohimeHatjYj1uvcqCjnzdg8KUvTsWVeuzQfR?filename=7r7UH2M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7r7UH2M.png&h=6afa4dac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaPjL1P7S8Snj2byQ1kD2MEFZzTbX8wXsnaJf7R6ZKE2c?filename=ZFaWbWb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFaWbWb.png&h=73ea5442&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然外賣個樣難睇左少少🤏但係味道依然好好，整體保留到8成。<br />\n<br />\n蕃薯整嘅薯條，應該係乜幾多間，雖然外賣關係軟腍左，但都食得出好新鮮，蕃薯味好甜。而真薯條就不過不失，個人愛蕃薯比較多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個包牛味十足，整體上唔會有違和感，可以一口食到所有材料，大細岩岩好。<br />\n我叫果個係大菇牛堡，入口你會食到好重嘅牛味，之後啡菇嘅甜味不經意慢慢中和牛味，再揮發出菇嘅甜香味，中和左和牛嘅油膩感。<br />\n口感上塊牛排唔會太散，又唔會好似麥記咁假，無加任何黏合劑，之後就係菇同菜嘅爽脆，加上幾滴汁水滲出來，味覺猶如高潮般衝突。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以劉浩龍嘅標準，絕對係一個食完會掛住嘅漢堡包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜嘅係可能太好生意太忙，幫襯左幾次感覺佢地話事人都唔太有禮貌，但做街坊生意要求唔太高。<br />\n<br />\n埋單80蚊，接受到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5c2bc50b811799a9c06d8fc2823261ced2b23b","tid":2471293,"uid":98810,"like":29,"dislike":4,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T12:11:33.000Z","msg":"鬍鬚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1523efa38618d169d25640f2121ff648ac3339bc","tid":2471293,"uid":98291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T12:35:42.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"881f01f61846d0396b11