"f84b9dd888142210295bd19c8f602a4d8cbe32ec","tid":2471293,"uid":39019,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"47bfe5479eb99f41bef3c8159053a7290f48357e","tid":2471293,"uid":339805,"like":5,"dislike":71,"score":-66,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T16:04:50.000Z","msg":"Shake shack<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T16:06:57.000Z","msg":"黑心 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T19:06:28.000Z","msg":"咪咁撚肉酸喇死乞衣<br />\n全世界得香港有咩<br />\n香港未有之前未撚去過日本同英國食？"},{"pid":"328d8a481ff4f028e7d7e5cbcbf3f41b07a2e327","tid":2471293,"uid":37008,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T19:20:03.000Z","msg":"Burger Joys (Best)<br />\nElectric Ave<br />\nHonbo<br />\n肥媽-鳩砌 （港式）<br />\nNomad Burger (ok)<br />\n5019<br />\nThe big bites<br />\nMoo Moo<br />\nThe Basic (ok)<br />\nBurger Land<br />\nBeeger<br />\nC+<br />\nLot On possession <br />\n<br />\n利申 要求唔高 全部都算好食嘅"},{"pid":"eadf9620b757f830f8f65bde4fddfdd44e8791a7","tid":2471293,"uid":215555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2196e9f925ab9d9c0543d1d043f10194b072d94","tid":2471293,"uid":220794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T12:05:51.000Z","msg":"最近睇劉浩龍同埋Eric Kwok 介紹漢堡包，<br />\n睇完心思思都想食，於是乎就揀左 鄰居。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7r7UH2M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7r7UH2M.png&h=6afa4dac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZFaWbWb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFaWbWb.png&h=73ea5442&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然外賣個樣難睇左少少🤏但係味道依然好好，整體保留到8成。<br />\n<br />\n蕃薯整嘅薯條，應該係乜幾多間，雖然外賣關係軟腍左，但都食得出好新鮮，蕃薯味好甜。而真薯條就不過不失，個人愛蕃薯比較多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個包牛味十足，整體上唔會有違和感，可以一口食到所有材料，大細岩岩好。<br />\n我叫果個係大菇牛堡，入口你會食到好重嘅牛味，之後啡菇嘅甜味不經意慢慢中和牛味，再揮發出菇嘅甜香味，中和左和牛嘅油膩感。<br />\n口感上塊牛排唔會太散，又唔會好似麥記咁假，無加任何黏合劑，之後就係菇同菜嘅爽脆，加上幾滴汁水滲出來，味覺猶如高潮般衝突。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以劉浩龍嘅標準，絕對係一個食完會掛住嘅漢堡包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜嘅係可能太好生意太忙，幫襯左幾次感覺佢地話事人都唔太有禮貌，但做街坊生意要求唔太高。<br />\n<br />\n埋單80蚊，接受到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T04:45:12.000Z","msg":"重點你都無講出黎。係黃店呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271858e607f56989c01ec9624a8eb4ea39526a90","tid":2471293,"uid":2151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7088fed62a1c0c41ead135aaef40f43d4e8ca30e","tid":2471293,"uid":362707,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T20:26:09.000Z","msg":"深水埗 大角咀 BURGERMAN"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T06:00:09.000Z","msg":"食過兩三次大角咀 深水埗食過一次 <br />\n大角咀果間好食啲 食深水埗果次已經係兩點半 唔係咩繁忙時間 薯條都可以炸到接近燶 反而塊肉煎到唔夠火候 咁嘅價位<br />\n食oh my dog好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"042b9bbd7499dbc380de7d9c9cb7c5c35983a64b","tid":2471293,"uid":362707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"271858e607f56989c01ec9624a8eb4ea39526a90","tid":2471293,"uid":2151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7088fed62a1c0c41ead135aaef40f43d4e8ca30e","tid":2471293,"uid":362707,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T20:26:09.000Z","msg":"深水埗 大角咀 BURGERMAN"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T06:00:09.000Z","msg":"食過兩三次大角咀 深水埗食過一次 <br />\n大角咀果間好食啲 食深水埗果次已經係兩點半 唔係咩繁忙時間 薯條都可以炸到接近燶 反而塊肉煎到唔夠火候 咁嘅價位<br />\n食oh my dog好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T06:12:42.000Z","msg":"深水埗一時時，有時好新鮮"},{"pid":"130c0a3f09e35820a4a259b76114a34083efd188","tid":2471293,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47bfe5479eb99f41bef3c8159053a7290f48357e","tid":2471293,"uid":339805,"like":5,"dislike":71,"score":-66,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T16:04:50.000