整體上唔會有違和感，可以一口食到所有材料，大細岩岩好。<br />\n我叫果個係大菇牛堡，入口你會食到好重嘅牛味，之後啡菇嘅甜味不經意慢慢中和牛味，再揮發出菇嘅甜香味，中和左和牛嘅油膩感。<br />\n口感上塊牛排唔會太散，又唔會好似麥記咁假，無加任何黏合劑，之後就係菇同菜嘅爽脆，加上幾滴汁水滲出來，味覺猶如高潮般衝突。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以劉浩龍嘅標準，絕對係一個食完會掛住嘅漢堡包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜嘅係可能太好生意太忙，幫襯左幾次感覺佢地話事人都唔太有禮貌，但做街坊生意要求唔太高。<br />\n<br />\n埋單80蚊，接受到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T06:42:17.000Z","msg":"Neighbour<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c2f1bf5363cd4be9a1a87637751a793ddf46d7","tid":2471293,"uid":22210,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T06:43:37.000Z","msg":"長沙灣Neighbour<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6be4d842b6897dc8b96644c632cd842409fc11f","tid":2471293,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T11:50:10.000Z","msg":"Hero's Friday"},{"pid":"7d52c821ec60cd074c8eec2f19ed3f845623a4a6","tid":2471293,"uid":33143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T19:00:07.000Z","msg":"鐘意食茶記burger多啲<br />\n美式我反而麻麻 有時疊得高唔可以一口塞落嘴到<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前食過灣仔間新嘉美都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad87c37baa51086a8d4c460ad2f487a83dcac631","tid":2471293,"uid":193440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T19:02:52.000Z","msg":"dr.burger 正呀"},{"pid":"e8e54d0768d369fc57919b6321aa33e878adc020","tid":2471293,"uid":91897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6be4d842b6897dc8b96644c632cd842409fc11f","tid":2471293,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T11:50:10.000Z","msg":"Hero's Friday"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T19:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa